      "description": "This car is in mint condition. It shows no meaningful signs of wear \u2014 the exterior is clean with no scratches, dents, or blemishes, and the interior is equally well-preserved. Mechanically, everything functions as it should with no known issues. A straightforward, well-kept example.",
